   Spawn: 
      RFR1 AA 3 A_Wander
	  TNT1 A 0 A_Look
	  RFR1 BB 3 A_Wander
	  TNT1 A 0 A_Look
	  RFR1 CC 3 A_Wander
	  TNT1 A 0 A_Look
	  RFR1 DD 3 A_Wander
	  TNT1 A 0 A_Look
      Loop 
   See: 
